    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《13柱庭》Demo，一个以RPG英雄养成为核心的多人肉鸽自走棋游戏！在这里，每一局都是一次全新的探索，每一次选择都关乎胜负。你将从多位风格迥异的传奇英雄中择一启程，组建独一无二的队伍，在动态变化的战场上与其他玩家展开对决，体验以英雄为核心的深度肉鸽自走棋乐趣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br>【你可以在体验版DEMO中游玩的是……】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅开放训练场模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6个特定英雄（正式版将开放超过20个英雄）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放部分棋子、天赋以及事件</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄为王，缔造传奇</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从超过20位能力超凡的传奇英雄中，选择你的命运化身。每位英雄不仅是一个棋子，更是一个完整的玩法核心与成长史诗。独特的技能树、专属的羁绊组合以及天赋，将彻底定义你的战略蓝图。是召唤亡灵大军、构筑虫族狂潮，还是打造机械洪流？你的英雄，即是传奇的开端。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/3725d73f1d99c1dbbfdd39c480a0d553.poster.avif?t=1772078423\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/3725d73f1d99c1dbbfdd39c480a0d553.webm?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/3725d73f1d99c1dbbfdd39c480a0d553.mp4?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富内容，海量组合</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内含300多个特性各异的棋子，它们与60多种可叠加强化的天赋，以及40多个能瞬间改变战局的随机事件交织互动。与超过20位核心英雄的能力产生化学反应，创造出近乎无限的战术组合。每一局，你都能探索新的致胜之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/844a532b3b1ec5a699893842ac685014.poster.avif?t=1772078423\" width=1170 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/844a532b3b1ec5a699893842ac685014.webm?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/844a532b3b1ec5a699893842ac685014.mp4?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/6382a2997c2a844f67c9276fa7b0495a.poster.avif?t=1772078423\" width=1170 height=612 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/6382a2997c2a844f67c9276fa7b0495a.webm?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/6382a2997c2a844f67c9276fa7b0495a.mp4?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度肉鸽，重复游玩</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有两局完全相同的游戏。每场对局，你都会遇到不同的随机事件、随机棋子和天赋。通过巧妙的组合，将看似普通的棋子与英雄能力、随机增益融合，创造出碾压对手的梦幻COMBO。每一次重开，都是发现新战术的绝佳机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/e5bd04def35fef0cf0c81d8bbc86feb9.poster.avif?t=1772078423\" width=1170 height=612 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/e5bd04def35fef0cf0c81d8bbc86feb9.webm?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/e5bd04def35fef0cf0c81d8bbc86feb9.mp4?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >异步对战，运筹帷幄</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用精心设计的异步对战系统，为您带来纯粹而深度的策略竞技体验。告别手速焦虑与实时反应压力，这里只比拼真正的智慧与构筑艺术。您拥有充裕的时间审慎思考、精密计算、推演阵容，在每一次交易棋子、每一个天赋选择、每一次阵型调整上都做到极致。在公平的思考环境中，精心打磨您的完美阵容，向13柱庭发起最稳健的冲击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/9865d797b20d3225065280da57d37e9d.poster.avif?t=1772078423\" width=1170 height=612 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/9865d797b20d3225065280da57d37e9d.webm?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304630/extras/9865d797b20d3225065280da57d37e9d.mp4?t=1772078423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入《13柱庭》官方QQ群：1075044719</strong></p>",
